sequenceDiagram
  actor A as 管理员
  participant V as 入住登记页
  participant API as elderCareApi
  participant DB as MySQL

  A->>V: 填写老人信息并选床位
  V->>API: POST /api/customers/checkin
  API->>DB: INSERT customer
  API->>DB: UPDATE bed 占用
  API->>DB: INSERT beddetails
  opt 设置护理级别
    API->>DB: UPDATE level_id
  end
  API-->>V: 客户对象
  V-->>A: 列表刷新
